lor: rgb(187, 246, 255);\"><em>is a 1st year high school girl and also a street performer. She is seen performing a street performance using puppets. The story she always brings during puppet shows is the Little Mermaid.</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/TShg-ko3Gu-F9EiqnPIjE.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/Vb4bE8PHNZDqD0Li-PsWs.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 212, 251);\"><em>Yes, there's no live as a Phantom Thieves. By the default, you are 2nd year high school student. </em></span><span style=\"color: rgb(71, 194, 255);\"><em>Miyu</em></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 212, 251);\"><em> will call you Onii-sama or Onee-sama depending on your gender. (If you asking me, why I use Onii/Onee-sama instead of Big Bro/Sis? Cause I'm weeb &amp; her voice in game literally calling player Onii-sama)</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/tNQxfogiPTQ1j_IyR7ua_.webp\" style=\"width: 286.5px; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(71, 194, 255);\"><em>Miyu</em></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 212, 251);\"><em> </em></span><span style=\"color: rgb(187, 246, 255);\"><em>is a daughter of a House of Representatives member. She ran away from home and chose to become a street performer to get away from her parents. </em></span><span style=\"color: rgb(71, 194, 255);\"><em>Miyu</em></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 212, 251);\"><em> </em></span><span style=\"color: rgb(187, 246, 255);\"><em>is always seen carrying a suitcase and bag wherever she goes. Her stage name for street puppetry is Kurage. (You can improve her relationship with her parents, or even distance her from her parents)</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/TShg-ko3Gu-F9EiqnPIjE.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/07DDydeSpNN","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"uZNRnWe31zRXBCCxcFpCL.webp","creator":"Rj_MH","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","📚 Fictional","🎮 Game","👤 AnyPOV"],"chats":37,"messages":542,"created_at":"2026-03-08T08:48:02.300197+00:00"}